    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Protecting Youth from Solitary Confinement Act </b></p> <p>This bill amends the federal criminal code to prohibit solitary confinement for juveniles in federal custody at juvenile facilities. </p> <p>The Bureau of Prisons must report on the rate of juvenile solitary confinement and the trends demonstrated by analyzing data for each juvenile who was subject to solitary confinement. </p>]]></text>
